text: José Alexis Armenteros Suárez (born December 13, 1992) is a Cuban judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the third round by Ramadan Darwish. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Cuba Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in judo Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Cuba Category:Judoka at the 2015 Pan American Games
